  <h2>
    <span class="">以下豆列推荐</span>
      &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;
      <span class="pl">&nbsp;(
          <a href="https://book.douban.com/subject/3806060/doulists">全部</a>
        ) </span>

  </h2>


    <div id="db-doulist-section" class="indent">
      <ul class="bs">
          <li class=""><a class="" href="https://www.douban.com/doulist/168129/" target="_blank">商务印书馆学术书单行本——五颜六色</a>
                <span class="pl">(休小谟)</span>
            </li>
          <li class=""><a class="" href="https://www.douban.com/doulist/1129694/" target="_blank">《如何阅读一本书》推荐书目</a>
                <span class="pl">(glassheart)</span>
            </li>
          <li class=""><a class="" href="https://www.douban.com/doulist/216900/" target="_blank">《如何阅读一本书》推荐书目1（慢慢更新）</a>
                <span class="pl">(爱读书的小兔兔)</span>
            </li>
          <li class=""><a class="" href="https://www.douban.com/doulist/1730403/" target="_blank">古典政治哲学的气息</a>
                <span class="pl">(恪彥)</span>
            </li>
          <li class=""><a class="" href="https://www.douban.com/doulist/41155218/" target="_blank">37°暖书单（一）</a>
